Example:
    rails g kit "button"
    rails g kit "status banner" --category=alerts_and_dialogs --description="Status banner for page-level notices" --rails --react --props variant:enum:info,warning dismissed:boolean

Prop format:
    name:type
    name:enum:value_one,value_two

